We previously reported this in https://github.com/aspnet/AspNetCore/issues/6097 and now we have been able to track down where problem happens.

A stack dump reveals that the access violation happens in HashProviderCng.cs https://github.com/dotnet/corefx/blob/154c2a35d5480d359729959f3e3e7d8578a18612/src/Common/src/Internal/Cryptography/HashProviderCng.cs):
